column1: Kamala like Joe Biden knows that working families need to put food on the table and the two of them know how to deliver economic security for all Americans.
Kamala Harris is a strong voice for the future of our party and our country. She's a westerner who has taken on special interests and knows how to fight for families living paycheck to paycheck.
